      "creatureType": "",
      "blurb": "Variant devilfish",
      "publicNotes": "<h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p><strong>Role (B1/B3):</strong> a <strong>variant devilfish</strong> grown enormous on the site's leaking magic — storm-swept into the Mushfens decades ago, too big now to return to the sea. He ate boggards until they knelt, then spent decades as their living god; Ileosa's charm demoted him from god to <strong>guard dog</strong>. He attacks intruders in the flooded entrance hall (B1) on sight, jets to engage, and pursues through every flooded space. His worship-tribute hoard fills his nest at B3.</p>",
